metadata.name: DIM_DATE
metadata.comment: Calendar dimension that shows all calendar attributes for a given calendar date from 2019 - 2035

DIM_DATE_SK.name: DIM_DATE_SK
DIM_DATE_SK.comment: Primary Key for Calendar Dimension for each Day

CLNDR_DAY_NM.name: CLNDR_DAY_NM
CLNDR_DAY_NM.comment: Name of the Calendar Date (e.g. SUNDAY, MONDAY, etc.)

CLNDR_MTH_NM.name: CLNDR_MTH_NM
CLNDR_MTH_NM.comment: Name of the month for the Calendar Date (e.g. JANUARY, FEBRUARY, etc.)

CLNDR_DAY_OF_WK.name: CLNDR_DAY_OF_WK
CLNDR_DAY_OF_WK.comment: Integer value calendar Day of the Week from 1- 7 where 1 is Sunday, 2 is Monday, etc.

CLNDR_DAY_OF_MTH.name: CLNDR_DAY_OF_MTH
CLNDR_DAY_OF_MTH.comment: Integer value of the day within the month (e.g. 28, 29, 30)

CLNDR_MTH_OF_YR.name: CLNDR_MTH_OF_YR
CLNDR_MTH_OF_YR.comment: Integer value fo the Fiscal Month Name for the Calendar Date in the Fiscal Year (1 is January, 2 is February, 3 is March, etc.)

CLNDR_YR_QTR.name: CLNDR_YR_QTR
CLNDR_YR_QTR.comment: String composite of the Calendar Days Year and Quarter (e.g. 2020Q1, 2020Q2, 2020Q3, etc.)

CLNDR_YR_MTH.name: CLNDR_YR_MTH
CLNDR_YR_MTH.comment: Integer composite of the Calendar Days Year and Month (e.g. 202012, 202101, 202102, etc.)

FISC_YR.name: FISC_YR
FISC_YR.comment: Integer Fiscal Year for the Calendar Date (e.g. 2020, 2021, 2022)

FISC_DAY_OF_YR.name: FISC_DAY_OF_YR
FISC_DAY_OF_YR.comment: Integer Fiscal Day Of the Year for the Calendar Date (e.g. 1, 2, … 365, etc.)

FISC_DAY_NM.name: FISC_DAY_NM
FISC_DAY_NM.comment: Fiscal Day Name of the Calendar Date (e.g. SUNDAY, MONDAY, etc.)

FISC_WK_OF_YR.name: FISC_WK_OF_YR
FISC_WK_OF_YR.comment: Integer value of the Fiscal Week in the Year for a Calendar Date (e.g. 49, 50, 51, 52, etc.)

FISC_WK_OF_PRD.name: FISC_WK_OF_PRD
FISC_WK_OF_PRD.comment: Integer value of the Fiscal Week in the Period for a Calendar Date (e.g. 49, 50, 51, 52, etc.)

FISC_MTH_OF_YR.name: FISC_MTH_OF_YR
FISC_MTH_OF_YR.comment: Integer value fo the Fiscal Month Name for the Calendar Date in the Fiscal Year (1 is January, 2 is February, 3 is March, etc.)

FISC_MTH_NM.name: FISC_MTH_NM
FISC_MTH_NM.comment: Name of the Fiscal Month for the Calendar Date (e.g. JANUARY, FEBRUARY, etc.)

FISC_QTR_OF_YR.name: FISC_QTR_OF_YR
FISC_QTR_OF_YR.comment: String value of the Fiscal Quarter for the Calendar Date (e.g. Q1, Q2, Q3, Q4)

FISC_HALF_OF_YR.name: FISC_HALF_OF_YR
FISC_HALF_OF_YR.comment: String value of the Fiscal Half for the Calendar Date (e.g. H1, H2)

FISC_YR_QTR.name: FISC_YR_QTR
FISC_YR_QTR.comment: String composite of the Fiscal Year and Fiscal Quarter for the Calendar Date (e.g. 2020Q1, 2020Q2, 2020Q3, etc.)

FISC_YR_MTH.name: FISC_YR_MTH
FISC_YR_MTH.comment: Integer composite of the Fiscal Year and Fiscal Month for the Calendar Date (e.g. 202012, 202101, 202102, etc.)

FISC_YR_WK.name: FISC_YR_WK
FISC_YR_WK.comment: Integer composite of the Fiscal Year and Fiscal Week for the Calendar Date (e.g. 202022, 202023, 202024, etc.)

FISC_WKS_THIS_PD.name: FISC_WKS_THIS_PD
FISC_WKS_THIS_PD.comment: Integer value that shows total number of Fiscal Weeks within the Period

TM_SK_YRAGO.name: TM_SK_YRAGO
TM_SK_YRAGO.comment: Same Day Prior Year for a given Calendar Date surrogate key

CLNDR_DT_YRAGO.name: CLNDR_DT_YRAGO
CLNDR_DT_YRAGO.comment: Same Day Prior Year for a given Calendar Date

FISC_PRD_NM.name: FISC_PRD_NM
FISC_PRD_NM.comment: Fiscal Period Name for a given Period

GRG_CLNDR_DT_YRAGO.name: GRG_CLNDR_DT_YRAGO
GRG_CLNDR_DT_YRAGO.comment: Same Day Prior Year for a given Calendar Date in the Gregorian Calendar

CLNDR_WK_STRT_DT.name: CLNDR_WK_STRT_DT
CLNDR_WK_STRT_DT.comment: Week Start Date for the Calendar Date

CLNDR_WK_END_DT.name: CLNDR_WK_END_DT
CLNDR_WK_END_DT.comment: Calendar Week End Date for the Calendar Date

CLNDR_WK_NM.name: CLNDR_WK_NM
CLNDR_WK_NM.comment: String Composite that shows the Week Start Date and Week End Date (e.g. 05/16/2021 - 05/22/2021)

CLNDR_MTH_NM_YR.name: CLNDR_MTH_NM_YR
CLNDR_MTH_NM_YR.comment: String composite of the Calendar Month Name with the Calendar Year (e.g. MARCH 2022, APRIL 2022, etc.)

GRG_CLNDR_YR_MTH_YRAGO.name: GRG_CLNDR_YR_MTH_YRAGO
GRG_CLNDR_YR_MTH_YRAGO.comment: Same Month Prior Year for a given Calendar Date in the Gregorian Calendar

FST_BUS_DT_NEXT_MONTH.name: FST_BUS_DT_NEXT_MONTH
FST_BUS_DT_NEXT_MONTH.comment: Date value for the first business day of the next Month for a given calendar date

MON_AFTER_LIC_THURS_DT.name: MON_AFTER_LIC_THURS_DT
MON_AFTER_LIC_THURS_DT.comment: Monday after Last Invoice Cost Thursday Date

CLNDR_DT_WKAGO.name: CLNDR_DT_WKAGO
CLNDR_DT_WKAGO.comment: Same Day Prior Week for a given calendar date
